<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 12:20:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储会议纪要让局势平静下来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-04/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 11:09:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>花旗计划在 2024 年底前成立中国投资银行部门并新聘 30 名员工 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citi-targets-china-investment-bank-unit-launch-30-new-hires-by-end-2024-source-2024-01-04/</link><description>一位直接知情人士表示，花旗集团计划最早在今年年底推出其全资中国投资银行部门，并为该业务招聘约 30 名员工。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citi-targets-china-investment-bank-unit-launch-30-new-hires-by-end-2024-source-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国“冰城”哈尔滨元旦假期游客量创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ice-city-harbin-draws-record-tourists-over-new-year-holiday-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国东北黑龙江省的冰雪之都哈尔滨的“冰城”在新年假期吸引了创纪录的游客数量，其中许多人被一年一度的冰雪节宏伟而复杂的冰雕所吸引。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ice-city-harbin-draws-record-tourists-over-new-year-holiday-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平就“恐怖袭击”向伊朗总统表示慰问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-sends-condolences-iran-president-terrorist-attack-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国国家电视台中央电视台称，中国国家主席习近平周四就一天前发生的“恐怖袭击”向伊朗总统致唁电。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 09:56:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-sends-condolences-iran-president-terrorist-attack-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>预计到 2024 年底，中国国际航班数量将达到新冠肺炎疫情前水平的 80%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sees-international-flights-reaching-80-pre-covid-levels-by-end-2024-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国航空监管机构周四表示，预计到今年年底，每周往返中国的国际航班数量将达到每周 6,000 架次，约为疫情前水平的 80%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 08:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sees-international-flights-reaching-80-pre-covid-levels-by-end-2024-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国的目标是更好地整合电动汽车和电网来管理电力需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-targets-better-integration-evs-grids-manage-power-demand-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国国家规划部门发布了加强新能源汽车与电网融合的新规定，因为全球最大的电动汽车（EV）市场旨在在向可再生能源过渡的过程中管理其电力需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 08:36:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-targets-better-integration-evs-grids-manage-power-demand-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>流弹造成五人受伤 中国向缅甸提出抗议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/artillery-shells-restive-myanmar-region-hit-southwest-china-town-global-times-2024-01-04/</link><description>外交部发言人周四表示，中国已就缅甸执政军政府与叛乱组织之间的战斗中炮弹误入边境附近一座小镇造成五人受伤一事向缅甸提出抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 07:16:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/artillery-shells-restive-myanmar-region-hit-southwest-china-town-global-times-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>台湾发现更多中国气球，称其中一个气球飞越岛屿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-spots-more-chinese-balloons-says-one-flew-over-island-2024-01-04/</link><description>台湾国防部表示，周三又发现三个中国气球飞越台湾海峡，其中一个飞越台湾岛，这是台湾国防部连续第二天报告此类活动。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 03:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-spots-more-chinese-balloons-says-one-flew-over-island-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国多省警告大雾，上海数十个航班延误</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-provinces-warn-thick-fog-dozens-shanghai-flights-delayed-2024-01-04/</link><description>周四，中国多个省份的大雾导致能见度极低，高速公路关闭，上海出发的航班延误，并促使天气预报员发布一系列警告和咨询。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:17:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-provinces-warn-thick-fog-dozens-shanghai-flights-delayed-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国12月服务业活动增速为5个月来最快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-dec-services-activity-expands-quickest-pace-5-months-caixin-pmi-2024-01-04/</link><description>周四的一项私营部门调查显示，由于新业务的强劲增长，中国服务业活动以五个月来最快的速度扩张，将该行业的乐观程度提升至三个月高点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 01:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-dec-services-activity-expands-quickest-pace-5-months-caixin-pmi-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称将在投票后公布对中国涉嫌干预选举的分析</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-will-publish-analysis-chinas-alleged-election-interference-post-vote-2024-01-04/</link><description>台湾外交部长表示，正在记录其对中国据称试图干预下周选举的经历，并将在投票后不久发表分析。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 01:17:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-will-publish-analysis-chinas-alleged-election-interference-post-vote-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国在南海持续巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-conducts-patrols-south-china-sea-amid-ongoing-run-ins-2024-01-03/</link><description>南部战区表示，随着该地区因争议领土问题持续紧张局势，中国军队将于周三至周四在南海进行例行巡逻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 14:22:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-conducts-patrols-south-china-sea-amid-ongoing-run-ins-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司（Gazprom）打破向中国供应天然气的单日纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/russias-gazprom-breaks-daily-record-gas-supply-china-2024-01-03/</link><description>俄罗斯能源巨头俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司周三表示，前一天通过西伯利亚力量管道向中国供应天然气的日产量创下了新纪录。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 12:42:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/russias-gazprom-breaks-daily-record-gas-supply-china-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国最大的珍珠奶茶制造商蜜雪和古茗申请香港首次公开募股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-largest-bubble-tea-makers-mixue-guming-apply-hong-kong-ipo-2024-01-03/</link><description>随着这个快速增长行业的公司在激烈的竞争中积极扩张，包括蜜雪冰城和古茗在内的中国领先珍珠奶茶制造商正争相申请在香港首次发售股票。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 10:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-largest-bubble-tea-makers-mixue-guming-apply-hong-kong-ipo-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军方称与美国第二次南海联合巡逻正在进行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-says-second-joint-patrol-with-us-underway-south-china-sea-2024-01-03/</link><description>菲律宾军方在一份声明中表示，菲律宾和美国周三开始在南海进行为期两天的联合巡逻，此举可能会激怒中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:57:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-says-second-joint-patrol-with-us-underway-south-china-sea-2024-01-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>